arra: 40 50 90 
we can form 405090 which can be divsible by 3
output: true;

logic:
   num % 3 ==0 means divisible by 3;
   take remeainder from each and add it 
   if rem sum divisble by 3 or rem sum is 0 then its formation also divisble by zero

class Solution {
    public boolean isPossible(int[] arr) {
        // code here
        int sum=0;
        for(int num: arr){
            sum+=num%3;
        }
       
        return sum%3 ==0  || sum==0 ? true : false;
    }
}
